'''Hafizur Rahman''' (born [[September 21]], [[1959]]) is a former [[Bangladesh]]i [[cricket]]er who played in 2 [[One-day International|ODI]]s in 1986. A wicketkeeper, Rahman moved to the U.S. after retiring from international cricket.

